---
import Layout from "../layout/Layout.astro";
import GoBackButton from '../components/GoBackButton.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <GoBackButton />
  <section>
    <h1>Now</h1>
    <p>
      Last update: 2024-07-01 11:17 PM
    </p>
  </section>
  <article>
    <section>
      <h2>What am I coding?</h2>
      <p>
        I'm currently working as a software engineer at <a href="https://fireflies.ai">Fireflies.ai</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm also working on some side projects, such as:
        <ul>
          <li>Trying to maintain my blog and creating a writing habit</li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/noghartt/btree-rs">btree-rs</a>, a B+Tree implementation in Rust</li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/noghartt/6502">6502</a>, a MOS 6502 emulator written in Rust</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>What are my current interests?</h2>
      <p>
        I'm currently interested in learning more about the following topics:
        <ul>
          <li>Database</li>
          <li>Distributed Systems</li>
          <li>CPUs and Hardware</li>
          <li>Compilers and Programming Language Theory</li>
          <li>Web front-end frameworks</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>What am I doing now?</h2>
      <p>
        Some things that I'm doing now:
        <ul>
          <li>Practicing French every day</li>
          <li>Discovering new hobbies with my girlfriend</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>What am I reading now?</h2>
      <p>
        I'm currently interested in learning more about the following topics:
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com.br/Antifragile-Things-That-Gain-Disorder/dp/0812979680">
              Antifragile: Things That Gain from Disorder
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Demon-Haunted-World-Science-Candle-Dark/dp/0345409469">
              The Demon-Haunted World: Science as a Candle in the Dark
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-2x);
  }

  article section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing);
  }

  li {
    list-style-type: disc;
    margin-left: var(--spacing-2x);
  }
</style>